## This action will scale capital letters to
## the height of small letters
##-----------------------------------------------------
## Save rsb in F1
##
set F1 rsb            
##
##-----------------------------------------------------
## Calculate the scale as a percentage
##
set F0 [100*xheight/caps]
##
##-----------------------------------------------------
## Do the transformation
##
origin 0 0
stretch F0 F0
##
##-----------------------------------------------------
## Scale rsb
##
set rsb [F1*xheight/caps]
